00:42:37,320 --> 00:42:39,080
Kita bertemu di pemakaman.

352
00:42:39,520 --> 00:42:41,240
Aku Seo Gong-chul.

353
00:42:41,760 --> 00:42:43,240
Aku Park Choi–go.

354
00:42:43,480 --> 00:42:44,960
