392
00:44:49,720 --> 00:44:51,360
Keluar dari gedungku.

393
00:44:51,720 --> 00:44:53,120
Apa?

394
00:45:02,400 --> 00:45:04,560
Bo–a menggambar webtoon?

395
00:45:04,880 --> 00:45:06,280
